<div class="container section text-justify mb-10">
    <div class="container flex flex-row items-center mb-5 justify-between">
      <div class="container flex flex-row items-center">
        <div class="text-2xl textTitleSection text-left font-titleBasis underline decoration-solid text-(--color-textColorTitle) textTitleShadow">Pose Player</div>
        <a href="https://poseplayer.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <svg class="size-5 ml-2 fill-current hover:fill-(--color-buttonHover) will-change-transform animate-bounce" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><title>Open Pose Player in new tab</title><path d="M14,3V5H17.59L7.76,14.83L9.17,16.24L19,6.41V10H21V3M19,19H5V5H12V3H5C3.89,3 3,3.9 3,5V19A2,2 0 0,0 5,21H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,19V12H19V19Z" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <a href="https://github.com/Andrefe91/project_poseSketch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="h-10">
        <%= inline_svg_tag "icons/logo_githubRepository2.svg", alt: "github repository logo",
        class: "object-contain inline lg:hidden fill-textColor stroke-(--color-textColor) drop-shadow-lg/20 hover:drop-shadow-xl hover:drop-shadow-emerald-300" %>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="container flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
        <div class="container lg:max-w-3/8 ">
            <p>I needed a simple tool for gesture drawing practice but couldn&#39t find anything that wasn&#39t bloated with features I didn&#39t need or required creating accounts I didn&#39t want. So I built one.
            </p>

            <p>Pose Player lets you load your own images, display them in a clean grid, and cycle through them with simple clicks or keyboard shortcuts. You can adjust timing for timed sessions, randomize the order, or jump to specific images when you need to focus on particular poses. No cloud storage, no tracking, no sign-ups, just your images on your device, displayed exactly the way you want them.
            </p>

            <p>Built with React and vanilla JavaScript because sometimes the best solution is the straightforward one. It does exactly what it needs to do, nothing more, and it&#39s free for anyone who wants to use it.</p>


            <div class="container flex justify-center">
                <a href="https://github.com/Andrefe91/project_poseSketch" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <%= inline_svg_tag "icons/logo_githubRepository2.svg", alt: "github repository logo",
                class: "object-contain hidden lg:inline lg:h-13 fill-textColor stroke-(--color-textColor) drop-shadow-lg/20 hover:drop-shadow-xl hover:drop-shadow-emerald-300" %>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-sm sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-6xl xl:max-w-8xl mx-auto space-y-4">
            <!-- Main Carousel -->
            <section id="main-carousel" class="overflow-hidden w-full" data-controller="carousel"
            data-carousel-loop-value="false"
            data-carousel-drag-free-value="false"
            data-carousel-dots-value="false"
            data-carousel-buttons-value="true">
            <div class="overflow-hidden outline-hidden mx-4 sm:mx-6 md:mx-8 cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing" data-carousel-target="viewport">
                <div class="flex">
                <div class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-full min-w-0 p-2 text-center rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/20 bg-neutral-50/10 relative select-none">
                    <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_1.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                </div>

                <div class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-full min-w-0 p-2 text-center rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/20 bg-neutral-50/10 relative select-none">
                    <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_2.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                </div>

                <div class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-full min-w-0 p-2 text-center rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/20 bg-neutral-50/10 relative select-none">
                    <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_3.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                </div>

                <div class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-full min-w-0 p-2 text-center rounded-xl border border-neutral-200/20 bg-neutral-50/10 relative select-none">
                    <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_4.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center mt-4 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 items-center">
                <button class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-full bg-(--color-button) p-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-800 shadow-xs hover:bg-(--color-buttonHover) outline-hidden border border-neutral-200 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" type="button" data-carousel-target="prevButton" aria-label="Previous">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-textColor size-4" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><g fill="currentColor"><path d="M11.5 16C11.308 16 11.116 15.9271 10.97 15.7801L4.71999 9.53005C4.42699 9.23705 4.42699 8.76202 4.71999 8.46902L10.97 2.21999C11.263 1.92699 11.738 1.92699 12.031 2.21999C12.324 2.51299 12.324 2.98803 12.031 3.28103L6.311 9.001L12.031 14.721C12.324 15.014 12.324 15.489 12.031 15.782C11.885 15.928 11.693 16.002 11.501 16.002L11.5 16Z"></path></g></svg>
                </button>

                <button class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center size-10 rounded-full bg-(--color-button) p-2 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-800 shadow-xs hover:bg-(--color-buttonHover) outline-hidden border border-neutral-200 disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed" type="button" data-carousel-target="nextButton" aria-label="Next">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-textColor size-4" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18"><g fill="currentColor"><path d="M13.28 8.46999L7.03 2.21999C6.737 1.92699 6.262 1.92699 5.969 2.21999C5.676 2.51299 5.676 2.98803 5.969 3.28103L11.689 9.001L5.969 14.721C5.676 15.014 5.676 15.489 5.969 15.782C6.115 15.928 6.307 16.002 6.499 16.002C6.691 16.002 6.883 15.929 7.029 15.782L13.279 9.53201C13.572 9.23901 13.572 8.76403 13.279 8.47103L13.28 8.46999Z"></path></g></svg>
                </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Thumbnail Carousel -->
            <section class="overflow-hidden w-full" data-controller="carousel"
                data-carousel-loop-value="false"
                data-carousel-drag-free-value="false"
                data-carousel-dots-value="false"
                data-carousel-buttons-value="false"
                data-carousel-thumbnails-value="true"
                data-carousel-main-carousel-value="main-carousel">
                <div class="overflow-hidden outline-hidden mx-4 sm:mx-6 md:mx-8 cursor-grab active:cursor-grabbing" data-carousel-target="viewport">
                <div class="flex">
                    <button class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-1/4 min-w-0 p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-neutral-600 dark:border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 relative select-none hover:border-neutral-700 dark:hover:border-neutral-300 outline-hidden" data-carousel-target="thumbnailButton">
                    <div class="aspect-auto rounded bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_1.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                    </div>
                    </button>
                    <button class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-1/4 min-w-0 p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 relative select-none hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 outline-hidden" data-carousel-target="thumbnailButton">
                    <div class="aspect-auto rounded bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_2.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                    </div>
                    </button>
                    <button class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-1/4 min-w-0 p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 relative select-none hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 outline-hidden" data-carousel-target="thumbnailButton">
                    <div class="aspect-auto rounded bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_3.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                    </div>
                    </button>
                    <button class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 md:mr-4 flex-shrink-0 flex-grow-0 basis-1/4 min-w-0 p-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 relative select-none hover:border-neutral-400 dark:hover:border-neutral-500 outline-hidden" data-carousel-target="thumbnailButton">
                    <div class="aspect-auto rounded bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <%= image_tag "tools/posePlayer/screenshot_4.png", alt:"PosePlayer webpage Screenshot", class: "" %>
                    </div>
                    </button>
                </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

